headline: STAG INDUSTRIAL ANNOUNCES PROMOTION OF STEVEN T. KIMBALL TO CHIEF OPERATING OFFICER
summary: STAG Industrial, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: STAG) today announced the promotion, effective August 1, 2025, of Steven T. Kimball to Chief Operating Officer.
